Report_availability - Class in com.net2plan.examples.ocnbook.reports
This report receives as an input a network design, the network recovery scheme algorithm, and the network risks (SRGs), and estimates the availability of the network (including individual availabilities for each demand), using an enumerative process that also provides an estimation of the estimation error.
Report_availability() - Constructor for class com.net2plan.examples.ocnbook.reports.Report_availability
 
Report_delay - Class in com.net2plan.examples.ocnbook.reports
This report receives as an input a network design, where the network is assumed to be based on packet switching, and estimates the packet delay of the different flows.
Report_delay() - Constructor for class com.net2plan.examples.ocnbook.reports.Report_delay
 
Report_perSRGFailureAnalysis - Class in com.net2plan.examples.ocnbook.reports
This report receives as an input a network design, the network recovery scheme algorithm, and a set of network risks (SRGs), and computes the availability of each network and each demand, in the no-failure state, and in each of the single-SRG failure states.
Report_perSRGFailureAnalysis() - Constructor for class com.net2plan.examples.ocnbook.reports.Report_perSRGFailureAnalysis
 
Report_WDM_lineEngineering - Class in com.net2plan.examples.general.reports
This report shows line engineering information for WDM links in a multilayer optical network.
Report_WDM_lineEngineering() - Constructor for class com.net2plan.examples.general.reports.Report_WDM_lineEngineering
 
Report_WDM_pointToPointLineEngineering - Class in com.net2plan.examples.general.reports
This report shows line engineering information for WDM links in the network.
Report_WDM_pointToPointLineEngineering() - Constructor for class com.net2plan.examples.general.reports.Report_WDM_pointToPointLineEngineering
 
Report_wdm_routingSpectrumAndModulationAssignments - Class in com.net2plan.examples.general.reports
This report collects information about the Routing and Spectrum assignment in the network, as well as other general information about the WDM layer.
Report_wdm_routingSpectrumAndModulationAssignments() - Constructor for class com.net2plan.examples.general.reports.Report_wdm_routingSpectrumAndModulationAssignments
